{
  "id": "RAW_ff984a5f",
  "title": "立省 499！我给你们找到了最傻瓜的 OpenClaw 安装方式。",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzIyMzA5NjEyMA==&mid=2647680547&idx=1&sn=1435bf3cfc3a5aebf18f75ffdce55b21",
  "date": "2026-03-10 02:04:00",
  "author": "数字生命卡兹克",
  "siteName": "数字生命卡兹克",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><img src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=18778d7b&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2F2jjfQoZLoqXgTicCUrSknWDMfPBpBDFUjNNFicu35GTAYOq0ZcL2zLPjvbWP3ojekCwIVAsMibLm11fjRuaJiauWSia0bCoQGn67FGCJweMpQXAU%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">OpenClaw卷麻了，真的卷麻了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我前几天写的那篇</span><a class=\"normal_text_link mp_article_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzIyMzA5NjEyMA==&amp;mid=2647680353&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=0ae2340edd5fa0c6076d9bd31c9e14e7&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"我花499找人上门安装OpenClaw，看到了AI时代最魔幻的一幕。\" data-itemshowtype=\"0\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我花499找人上门安装OpenClaw，看到了AI时代最魔幻的一幕。</span></a><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">都快几十万阅读了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">然后，就有很多人催我，问我啥时候再写一个小白也能上手的OpenClaw部署教程，他们也能出去给人安装挣钱。。。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我两眼一黑。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">但是其实也能看到更广阔的需求，很多人其实再说，你要是自己装不了，那基本也就根本不是OpenClaw的用户，我觉得这话其实不太对，因为从人机交互来说，有些事情你得解离来看。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">就像打印机这个事，安装就巨恶心，但是你敢说你在说公司里你没有打印需求吗。。。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">普通人，也值得体验Agent的魅力，从我的角度来说，OpenClaw其实是Clade Code和Codex的下位替代品，但是真的不是人人都能用的上Claude Code的，也不是人人都能用的懂命令行，所以能在一个聊天窗口里，体验一下Agent的魅力，哪有何乐而不为呢。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">所以其实我最近也在看，有没有更方便的、真的是傻瓜一键部署的方式。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">但是坦率的讲，之前找了两天没找到，都复杂，都麻烦。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">而且还要教大家装Skills，一想想，更麻烦了。。。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">直到，凌晨。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">智谱发了个东西，叫AutoClaw。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"500196898\" data-ratio=\"0.5787037037037037\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=26e987e5&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2F2jjfQoZLoqU8xJLF6JOWNdn4O1nlQt1X2Bon4fZNkgYEbpEL6WWpCJ6nVSjPJQ59hzxQ537VFGZAuRt6ibyPTX7Q1icicxE3YhoR7VUBEXJicME%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我觉得，我找到了，这就是现在最傻瓜、最简单、最离谱的OpenClaw的安装方式。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">而且，是本地的！是直接部署在你电脑上的小龙虾，不是那种云端的。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">且支持Mac和Win，同时优化了很多原版OpenClaw做了不好的skills和插件，Mac甚至可以通过智谱那个非常屌的browser use自动操控网页帮你全自动配置好飞书，我当时看到我人都懵了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">直接跟我们同事说，OpenClaw部署教程停了吧，明天公司的同事们直接就看这篇文章，直接装AutoClaw吧。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-backh=\"360\" data-backw=\"489\" data-imgfileid=\"500196890\" data-ratio=\"0.7361963190184049\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"489\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto !important;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=ef671608&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F2jjfQoZLoqVG5QoXnGqTuEQZsGicRXNzqof73t18iblTvcJ99CngdhQ5mbtbApsbW1AHDhhAzuh0TtNaJtR6SKLndibSWuib1SJiclhSdV2kbpo0%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">相信我，你看完了我这篇，你是真的立省499，任何人，我都保证你能最快速的用上OpenClaw。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">首先，打开AutoClaw的官网：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\"><a href=\"https://autoglm.zhipuai.cn/autoclaw/\" target=\"_blank\">https://autoglm.zhipuai.cn/autoclaw/</a></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我还是用Mac来做一下演示。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">下载安装包，打开，然后你就能看到一个登录界面了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6425925925925926\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500196858\" data-aistatus=\"1\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=ba9fbd93&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2F2jjfQoZLoqUTLzTzmTax9Xxx14vqtF0avogB0htZSIUhjn6pRamqAhnANaEyvmao6PWshOV0gWmicn10T4E94aCXDeBia20ztUVhXtcEk0qib4%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">直接用你的中国手机号登录，这一步我相信你们一定都超级熟悉对吧。。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">然后你就能进到这个界面了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6425925925925926\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500196860\" data-aistatus=\"1\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=85ac5f8b&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2F2jjfQoZLoqV1DB1Uw5JP1mibAuFzxBiaaqcOwPdPLvMWyNJbs19Po3k6BREFQfYD1hDib6wU9XiaVVHyRmfvg3zemWPO0NAa3ibZGO5qm8gPrjDo%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">其实，这个时候，你就已经可以在AutoClaw的界面里，跟小龙虾进行对话了，全都配置完了。。。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5145228215767634\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"723\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500196879\" data-aistatus=\"1\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=01b91790&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F2jjfQoZLoqVfJ5ZvOvjuSZxRn5cvrGXTeEQmZ3xlqdkV2ej6sEWspRC6CM92LR00NcwPfibibiaTYtAgdtZ9UEBdmkupBnGYCGribibgnKVib2ff8%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">对，已经可以用了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">当然，如果你还是喜欢在飞书里面用。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">那还是需要做两步配置，这块千万不要觉得，哎你不是说好特别简单吗，怎么还要配置。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这个配置，你相信我，究极简单。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">第一步，点击那个快速配置按钮。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: normal;\">输入你的名字和称呼，让小龙虾知道你是谁，工作目录那里不用管，但是那个限制文件访问范围，一定！一定！一定记得要跟我一样，是关闭状态，要不然这个小龙虾，真的就没啥用了，你电脑里的任何非工作目录里的东西都读取不了，就很伤。。。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.878140703517588\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"796\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500196861\" data-aistatus=\"1\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=50d008f1&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F2jjfQoZLoqV3iacALlGicO5v9iafV5uD2DEsicWLOicKRjPhzXS7YrgqtTTnicn8SeJAeWUib7os6EMibnU39Yf1P5CDzdzg5g74ZkcPku9Ko5qyP3c%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">搞定了以后，我们点完成配置，第一步就算完事了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">没错，就是这么简单。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">第二步，链接飞书。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: normal;\">我一定要让大家看看，这辈子我用过的，最丝滑的链接飞书的OpenClaw体验。。。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: normal;\">这尼玛才是AI啊。。。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: normal;\">点击一键接入飞书，你就能看到一个弹窗，点那个开始自动配置。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6955414012738853\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"785\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500196862\" data-aistatus=\"1\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=2b6d908d&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2F2jjfQoZLoqUQrmYorOfhyEiafDaSH0XkYB1Mrj2m56iadicQLMeUwhRPrvTLAuFRvD08ISHPIx6ToXj4fDtdiaPtE0iarDfkmhRc6pxiaJD8aKYtY%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: normal;\">当然，如果你是老玩家，已经有了飞书机器人的参数，你也可以点那个手动设置密钥，自己填一下。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.3498402555910543\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"626\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500196864\" data-aistatus=\"1\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=629105c1&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2F2jjfQoZLoqVk3dABh7oM4Bice2OCSbiaGeicyoFrbPCyk7Uep9beIkwk9lSpzsefsUI4Bh69BUGSTTPCVZ7TzPySyuBVobVd2qCYAGVyRXF78E%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">但是大多数朋友，既然看这篇文章，估计也不知道怎么弄。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">那你就点自动就好。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">点了以后，AutoClaw会自动打开一个浏览器，让你扫码登录飞书，记得用手机飞书扫一下。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6518518518518519\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500196866\" data-aistatus=\"1\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=5d9cf7b0&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F2jjfQoZLoqXtHfwicjTdZ60oIH7Fy0iaDHAD8dcs1RhvYDdGx0IUojICz8Ga4EKz0eAmH2W05JZN5uAnCicP7gu3DjrpggBFxGqSyon7QMaeP8%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">然后，你就可以享受一下，什么叫自动化的乐趣。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我录了个视频，不要眨眼。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">一共45秒，AI全自动配置，我对着玉皇大帝和耶稣共同发誓，我一秒没剪一秒没有加速，我甚至第一次都没看清它干了啥。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这哥们，就直接给我配置完了飞书。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">不是，我是真的懵了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">太牛逼了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">智谱也是挺骚的，这块应该是把RPA拿过来用了，因为飞书配置就是纯粹的固定流程识别元素+全自动点击，所以RPA是又稳又快。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">不过这个自动配置，仅限Mac，Windows没招，还是得手动一下，不过也不难，这块智谱也出了教程，大家跟着文档一步一步来就行，我就不复述了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text